ill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者設計部手足再改下d圖<br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/22P5zpN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F22P5zpN.jpg&h=30bad7ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9RoYUpO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9RoYUpO.png&h=4263cb48&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VFi904O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVFi904O.jpg&h=9a509a22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0HVWC9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0HVWC9.jpg&h=b9ba03e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OrPgC9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OrPgC9.png&h=e761163e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yV2ZDRv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyV2ZDRv.jpg&h=7b216b77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b03a5a1bed9fdce53519b7680bacf74d3d8f11f","tid":1433573,"uid":280452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:02:33.000Z","msg":"大把人爭住做喇<br />\n政府內部已經傾好大幅加差佬人工<br />\n<br />\n到時pc仔入職都三萬<br />\n香港人唔做 咪支那人得閒呃下OT 又每個月多十皮<br />\n做兩年已經買到樓 人生贏家<br />\n叫雞又唔使錢"},{"pid":"be35a2abef93796f1f5c8a37734cfe07716505a4","tid":1433573,"uid":112467,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c82ffc444934e92e8551c97afd1a3a5e69fc4e","tid":1433573,"uid":253418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:17:14.000Z","msg":"3皮幾，有宿舍，得閒拉9你，好L吸引喎"},{"pid":"56ca77b4973bc8e181f66b029b141078ca4054b3","tid":1433573,"uid":294402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:23:27.000Z","msg":"吓，好多智力有問題又搵唔到食衝到入去做，舊時就話查三代身家清唔清白，而家，可能查吓你有冇社團背景，有嘅即請。"},{"pid":"0661470a1ec3cecab8e182b584462a268b62f401","tid":1433573,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"依家專講黑社會背景"},{"pid":"b32c2752a571e84915cea627473023830c0a3682","tid":1433573,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:37:03.000Z","msg":"其實土生土長既香港人 應該唔會去做<br />\n最主要原因是, 香港人身邊有好多親戚朋友<br />\n如果佢地去做警察, 比親戚朋友知道, 就會同佢絕交<br />\n畢竟警察形象太低了<br />\n<br />\n將來警察可能會降低門檻, 唔洗學歷, 唔洗識流利廣東話都可以收<br />\n然後吸引大陸新移民 加入<br />\n<br />\n大陸人 無道德, 無底線, 佢地根本唔會理警察形象低, 有錢收就得<br />\n大陸公安,城管 形象更低, 一樣大把大陸人想去做<br />\n更何況警察 既人工,福利  比公安/城管更高<br />\n<br />\n到時候香港警察 真係可以正式變香港公安<br />\n首先治安會變差, 因為大陸公安 一向都唔會真心捉賊<br />\n你睇下大陸周街咁多小偷, 劫匪, 但從來唔會有公安去巡邏, 因為公安全部在公安局入面打緊牌, 唔得閒理你<br />\n<br />\n然後鎮壓手段會更狠<br />\n正如上面所講, 大陸人無道德, 無底線.......<br />\n香港警察 點衰都好, 都唔會打死你, 最多 打你幾棍發泄一下,再拘捕你<br />\n而大陸公安, 城管 直情是往死裡打, 打死人先肯停手"},{"pid":"629a6026aa7207e6bac4d45edce57cc04eb5d19c","tid":1433573,"uid":21699,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"太天真<br />\n運動完左香港人就唔記得哂<br />\n<br />\n上次雨傘高登都係吹到要殺警又盛 (e.g. 十人一組, 十人殺一警個post)<br />\n<br />\n結果雨革完左後, 一堆黃絲加入警隊, 然後變唒藍絲<br />\n<br />\n基本上, 你個運動完左, 民氣失左, D人就會開始淡忘"},{"pid":"6af52938aee155f2abe3344bed183abb3a94dbb0","tid":1433573,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9313c5ff0e38c36830612a0d8b380ef7e6ad9ee8","tid":1433573,"uid":46511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T13:56:30.000Z","msg":"暗中請啲蚛蟈人/支那人入去做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:19:00.000Z","msg":"已經唔暗中"},{"pid":"b379ecbe7d927b8e9646469618a18fb20c35526d","tid":1433573,"uid":119653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b03a5a1bed9fdce53519b7680bacf74d3d8f11f","tid":1433573,"uid":280452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:02:33.000Z","msg":"大把人爭住做喇<br />\n政府內部已經傾好大幅加差佬人工<br />\n<br />\n到時pc仔入職都三萬<br />\n香港人唔做 咪支那人得閒呃下OT 又